

                    SETTINGS                                                                       EFFECT
Alt+Z  (make sure to set editor:wordwrap on settings)                           Use toggle wordwrap to fit the paragraph on the screen


                     PLUGINS                                                                        USE
                   Live Server                                                  Allows you to view see the realtime view of your site the moment  you save your file
                                                                                          (best combined with autosave) 


                EMMET ABBREVIATION                                                                    CODES
                        !                                                                  emmet code for adding the html beginning
                      
                       img                                                         <img src="URL"    Height=   Width=  Alt="image name">
                   
                     ctrl + /                                                                  make comments on your HTML <!-- -->
                    
                       a                                                        <a href="udemy.com" target="_blank">this is a udemy link</a> 
                                                                                  (Note. The target attribute will open the link in new tab)
                                                                                <a href="udemy.com"><img src="/images/download.png" width="200" alt=""></a>
										   (Note. add a link to an image) 
